item.title: Jared Allen signs one-day contract to retire as a Viking
item.description:
Jared Allen signs one-day contract to retire as a Viking

Jared Allen apparently rode his horse as far as the nearest snowmobile. The veteran defensive end, who finished last season with the Panthers, has signed a one-day contract with the Vikings to retire a member of the team he was best with. item.title: The Rams Trading For #1 Overall Means The Philly Media's Pipedream For Carson Wentz Should Be Shut Down
item.description:
The Rams Trading For #1 Overall Means The Philly Media's Pipedream For Carson Wentz Should Be Shut Down

PFT - The Tennessee Titans have traded the first overall pick to the Los Angeles Rams. Obviously, this means the Rams see a franchise quarterback in this draft, and they think that quarterback will lead them in their new hometown of Los Angeles for years to come.
